{"id":1169781,"date":[{"year":1998,"month":9,"day":27}],"page":"3","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"180","ytitle":"","mtitle":"萤火虫","ftitle":"——和怀宗","authors":["沈致远"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"沈致远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你是火在飞"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是飞行的冷火"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有最高的发光效率"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最聪明的人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也未能解出个中秘密"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好说你是腐草变的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻罗小扇扑你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"透明纱囊盛你"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想借你的光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点起脑海中的灯塔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注:萤火虫的英文名是Firefly，直译为火飞。它尾部发光的机制是低温氧化荧光，其效率高于现有的人造光源。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"附:怀宗原诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"萤火虫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人是宇宙思想的标本"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宇宙的昆虫是人的灵魂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"灵魂提着灯笼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"很轻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路亮闪　亮闪……"}]}